<TMPL_INCLUDE NAME="cat-top.inc">

<TMPL_LOOP NAME="BIBLIO_RESULTS">
	<TMPL_IF NAME="norequests">
	<TMPL_ELSE>
		<a href=request.pl?bib=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblionumber">><img height=42  WIDTH=120 BORDER="0"
		src="<TMPL_VAR name="themelang">/images/requests.gif" align="right" border="0"></a>
	</TMPL_IF>

	<font SIZE=6><em><TMPL_VAR NAME="title"> (<TMPL_VAR NAME="author">)
	<TMPL_VAR NAME="class"></em></font><p>
	<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" border="1" align="left" width="220">
	<!-----------------BIBLIO RECORD TABLE--------->
	<tr valign="top">
		
    <td bgcolor="#cccc99" background="/images/background-mem.gif"> <b>REGISTRO 
      DEL LIBRO<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblionumber"></b> </td>
	</tr>
	<tr valign="top">
		<td>
			<form action="/cgi-bin/koha/modbib.pl" method="post">
			<table width="100%" border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
				<tr>
					<td width="33%">
						<input type="hidden" name="bibnum" value="<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblionumber">">
						<input type="image" name="submit" value="modify" border="0" src="<TMPL_VAR NAME='interface'>/<TMPL_VAR name="theme">/images/fileopen.png"  width=32 hspace=0 vspace=0 border=0>
					</td>
					<td width="33%"><input type="image" name="delete" value="delete" border="0" src="<TMPL_VAR NAME='interface'>/<TMPL_VAR name="theme">/images/edittrash.png" width=32 hspace=0 vspace=0 border=0"></td>
					<td width="33%"><a href="MARCdetail.pl?bib=<TMPL_VAR name="biblionumber">">MARC</a></td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			</form>
			<br>
      <FONT SIZE=2  face="arial, helvetica"> <b>Subt&iacute;tulo:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="subtitle"><br>
      <b>Autor:</b> <a href=/cgi-bin/koha/search.pl?author=<TMPL_VAR
			NAME="author" ESCAPE=URL>><TMPL_VAR NAME="author"></a><br>
      <b>Autor Adicional:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="additional"><br>
      <b>T&iacute;tulo de Serie:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="seriestitle"><br>
      <b>Tema:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="subject"><br>
			<b>Copyright:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="copyrightdate"><br>
      <b>Notas:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="notes"><br>
      <b>T&iacute;tulo Unificado:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="unititle"><br>
      <b>Serie:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="serial"><br>
      <b>N&uacute;mero Total de Items:</b> <TMPL_VAR NAME="count"> 
      <p>
			</font>
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</TMPL_LOOP>
<!-- FIXME - The help box overflows on the right. I think this is
     because it is specified as "width=70%", which the browser
     interprets as 70% of the width of the browser window. However,
     leaving out the "width=70%" makes the help box abut the "biblio
     record" box. I think the fix is to put all three boxes in a
     table, for layout, and make the help box as wide as it wants to
     be. -->

<center>
<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=2>
	<tr bgcolor="#cccc99" background="/images/background-mem.gif">
		
      <td>Tipo de Item </td>
		
      <td>Clase</td>
		
      <td>Ubicaci&oacute;n</td>
		<td>Date Due</td>
		
      <td>Visto por &uacute;ltima vez</td>
		
      <td>C&oacute;digo</td>
		
      <td>Volumen</td>
	</tr>
	<TMPL_LOOP NAME="ITEM_RESULTS">
		<tr>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="itemtype"></td>
			<td><a href=/cgi-bin/koha/search.pl?dewey=<TMPL_VAR NAME="dewey" ESCAPE=URL>><TMPL_VAR NAME="class"></a></td>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="branchname"></td>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="datedue"></td>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="datelastseen"></td>
			<td><a href="/cgi-bin/koha/moredetail.pl?type=<TMPL_VAR NAME="type">&item=<TMPL_VAR NAME="itemnumber>&bib=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblionumber">&bi=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblioitemnumber">"><TMPL_VAR NAME="barcode"></a></td>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="volumeddesc"></td>
			<TMPL_IF NAME="type">
				<td>
					<a href=/cgi-bin/koha/maint/catmaintain.pl?type=fixitemtype&bi=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblioitemnumber">&item=<TMPL_VAR NAME="itemtype">>Fix Itemtype</a>
				</td>
			</TMPL_IF>
		</tr>
	</TMPL_LOOP>
	<TMPL_LOOP NAME="WEB_RESULTS">
		<tr>
			<td><TMPL_VAR NAME="itemtype"></td>
			<td>Website</td>
			<td>Online</td>
			
      <td>Disponible</td>
			<td></td>
			<td>
				<a href="/cgi-bin/koha/moredetail.pl?item=<TMPL_VAR NAME="itemnumber>&bib=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblionumber">&bi=<TMPL_VAR NAME="biblioitemnumber">">http://<TMPL_VAR NAME="url"></a>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</TMPL_LOOP>
</table>
<p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" width=70%>
	<tr valign="top">
		<td bgcolor="99cc33" background="/images/background-mem.gif" colspan="2">
			
        <p><b>AYUDA</b><br>
          <b>Actualizar Biblioteca para todos los Items:</b> Haga click en el 
          bot&oacute;n <b>Modificar</b> [izquierda] para amend la biblioteca. 
          Cualquier cambio que haga actualiar&aacute; el registro para todos los 
          &iacute;tems listados arriba. 
        <p> <b>Actualizando la Biblioteca s&oacute;lo para UNO o ALGUNOS Items:</b> 
          Si alguno de los &iacute;tems listados arriba necesitan una biblioteca 
          diferente, o est&aacute;n en una biblioteca incorrecta, debe usar el 
          proceso de <a href="/cgi-bin/koha/loadmodules.pl?module=acquisitions">adquisiciones</a> 
          para arreglar esto. Necesitar&aacute; "re-ordenar" los &iacute;tems, 
          y borrarlos de esta biblioteca.
        <p />
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
</center>
<br clear=all>
<p />

